title: Moneyline Monaco - Week 3 NFL Bets: Packers-Bucs, Bills-Dolphins, Ravens-Pats, Saints-Panthers
itunes:title: Moneyline Monaco - Week 3 NFL Bets: Packers-Bucs, Bills-Dolphins, Ravens-Pats, Saints-Panthers
description:
Alex Monaco shares his best bets for Week 3 of the NFL season including Aaron Rodgers and the Packers taking on Tom Brady and the Buccaneers, Josh Allen and the Bills vs. Tua Tagovailoa's Dolphins in a potential shootout, Jameis Winston and the Saints looking to stay ahead of the Baker Mayfield's Carolina Panthers in a divisional matchup, and Lamar Jackson and the Ravens facing off against Mac Jones, Bill Belichick and the Patriots. #Volume #herd #colincowherd
